Text: Lunch at Scott Chens Friday June thjoin the MS team in the nation for a fabulous lunch presents and reminiscing about the ride We are all meeting at Scott Chens San Felipe at San Felipe and Voss to celebrate with Jeff Skilling and our fantastic team Lunch begins at PM and we have some really exciting news to announce Please RSVP via email to Deb Gebhardt at your earliest convenience See You Soon Deb
